Ayubowan! (May you live long) !!
Welcome to Jetwing, the largest family of luxury hotels in Sri Lanka. With a history spanning nearly half a century, Jetwing Hotels, under the leadership of Chairman Shiromal Cooray, embodies the strength of family values and the warmth of Sri Lankan hospitality. The hotels are scattered across the resplendent island, offering a variety of experiences – from historical cities to rustic villages and mountain retreats to seaside havens. Embracing a spirit of respect, care, and compassion, Jetwing invites guests to not just visit, but to become a part of their family. The relationship formed with guests is cherished, and they are encouraged to return as family, as they experience the luxurious charm that sets Jetwing apart. Shiromal Cooray extends a warm welcome to explore the enchanting stories and wonders of Sri Lanka through the doors of Jetwing Hotels.
